{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8ee9eb19c5","title":"邀请伏罗希洛夫访问中国的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84bcb2a548","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":6,"articleId":"8ee9eb19c5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"2bb405da15","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1957年1月18日，伏罗希洛夫复信毛泽东。信中说：“我怀着感激的心情接受您的邀请。如果对您方便的话，我准备在1957年4月15日至5月5日期同访问兄弟般的中华人民共和国。"}],"contents":[{"id":"808c81305c","type":"title","text":"邀请伏罗希路天访向中国的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5"},{"id":"2bb405da15","type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃社会主义共和国联盟最高苏维埃主席团主席敬爱的伏罗希洛夫同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5"},{"id":"4047aeaf2a","type":"paragraph","text":"我代表中华人民共和国和中国人民热烈地邀请你，敬爱的主席同志来我国进行访问。我深信，你的访问必将进一步巩固和发展我们两国之间的亲密合作和伟大友谊。如你同意，请将你认为合适的访问日期，通知我们。我和全中国的人民以十分愉快的心情期待着你的光临。谨向你致最崇高的敬意","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5"},{"id":"bbc86a5c33","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国主席毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5"},{"id":"59f9dd5282","type":"paragraph","text":"1957年1月6日于北京","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5"}],"page":{"id":"06b0c95948","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"8ee9eb19c5","start":223,"end":223}}}},"__N_SSG":true}